<H1>Gods and Their Specialty Priests</H1>
<P>The many gods and goddesses of the Kitaran Sea region are as varied as the people
who worship them. In this section you will find descriptions of the priesthoods of
the gods, which is more important to life in the region than knowing about the gods
themselves...</P>
<P>Two of the most important gods in the campaign are <A HREF="tyr.html">Tyr</A>
and <A HREF="bane.html">Bane</A>. Worship of <B>Tyr</B> is the state religion
in Beogar, and the Beogarans claim that worship of <B>Bane</B> is the state religion
of Ket, which is not <I>quite</I> true.</P>
<P>Before you go to the priesthood descriptions, you may want to take a look at the
<A HREF="overview.html">overview</A>.</P>
<P><I>The arrows within this section will take you through the descriptions in alphabetical
order.</I></P>
